---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import StepCard from '../../../components/StepCard.astro';
---

<Layout title="在 macOS 安裝 OpenClaw" lang="zh" currentPath="/zh/guide/install-mac" description="在 macOS Monterey 以上使用 Homebrew 和 Node.js 安裝 OpenClaw 的完整步驟教學。">
  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="badge badge-orange">macOS 安裝指南</span>
      <h1>在 macOS 上安裝</h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">支援 macOS Monterey 及更新版本。透過 Homebrew 安裝 Node.js，再安裝 OpenClaw，幾分鐘內搞定。</p>
      <div class="lang-notice">
        <a href="/guide/install-mac">🇺🇸 Read in English</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="page-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">
        <aside class="toc">
          <div class="toc-inner">
            <div class="toc-title">本頁目錄</div>
            <ul>
              <li><a href="#requirements">系統需求</a></li>
              <li><a href="#homebrew">安裝 Homebrew</a></li>
              <li><a href="#nodejs">安裝 Node.js</a></li>
              <li><a href="#openclaw">安裝 OpenClaw</a></li>
              <li><a href="#setup">執行設定</a></li>
              <li><a href="#faq">常見問題</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </aside>

        <article class="article">
          <section id="requirements" class="article-section">
            <h2>系統需求</h2>
            <div class="requirements-grid">
              <div class="req-card">
                <div class="req-icon">🍎</div>
                <div class="req-label">macOS</div>
                <div class="req-value">Monterey 12+</div>
                <div class="req-note">Ventura、Sonoma、Sequoia 也支援</div>
              </div>
              <div class="req-card">
                <div class="req-icon">🟢</div>
                <div class="req-label">Node.js</div>
                <div class="req-value">v22 或以上</div>
                <div class="req-note">透過 Homebrew 安裝</div>
              </div>
              <div class="req-card">
                <div class="req-icon">🔑</div>
                <div class="req-label">API Key</div>
                <div class="req-value">建議使用 Anthropic</div>
                <div class="req-note">至 console.anthropic.com 取得</div>
              </div>
              <div class="req-card">
                <div class="req-icon">📦</div>
                <div class="req-label">磁碟空間</div>
                <div class="req-value">約 200 MB</div>
                <div class="req-note">Node.js + OpenClaw CLI</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section id="homebrew" class="article-section">
            <h2>第一步：安裝 Homebrew</h2>
            <p>
              <a href="https://brew.sh" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Homebrew</a>（Mac 上的免費「軟體安裝管家」）是 macOS 的標準套件管理工具。
              如果已安裝，直接跳到第二步。
            </p>
            <p>開啟 <strong>Terminal</strong>（按 <code>⌘ 空白鍵</code>，輸入「Terminal」），然後執行：</p>
            <pre><code>/bin/bash -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/HEAD/install.sh)"</code></pre>
            <p class="code-hint">⌨️ 複製貼上後，按 Enter 鍵確認執行</p>
            <p>腳本會要求你輸入 Mac 密碼，並在需要時安裝 Xcode Command Line Tools（Mac 的開發工具包，讓你的電腦能安裝和執行各種工具，免費的）。過程約需 3–5 分鐘。</p>

            <div class="terminal-preview">
              <div class="terminal-bar">
                <span class="dot dot-red"></span>
                <span class="dot dot-yellow"></span>
                <span class="dot dot-green"></span>
                <span class="terminal-title">Terminal — bash</span>
              </div>
              <pre class="terminal-body"><code><span class="t-prompt">$</span> /bin/bash -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/HEAD/install.sh)"
==> Checking for `sudo` access...
Password:
==> This script will install:
/usr/local/bin/brew
...
==> Installation successful!</code></pre>
            </div>

            <details class="advanced-details">
              <summary>🔧 進階說明：Apple Silicon 路徑資訊</summary>
              <div class="advanced-content">
                <strong>Apple Silicon（M1/M2/M3/M4）用戶：</strong>Homebrew 會安裝到 <code>/opt/homebrew/</code>，而不是 Intel Mac 的 <code>/usr/local/</code>。安裝程序會自動引導你設定 PATH。
              </div>
            </details>
          </section>

          <section id="nodejs" class="article-section">
            <h2>第二步：安裝 Node.js</h2>
            <p>Homebrew 安裝完成後，安裝 Node.js 22：</p>
            <pre><code>brew install node@22</code></pre>
            <p class="code-hint">⌨️ 複製貼上後，按 Enter 鍵確認執行</p>
            <p>連結並確認安裝：</p>
            <pre><code>brew link node@22 --force
node --version   # 應顯示 v22.x.x
npm --version    # 應顯示 10.x.x 以上</code></pre>
<p class="code-hint">⌨️ 複製貼上後，按 Enter 鍵確認執行</p>

            <div class="info-box">
              <span class="info-icon">💡</span>
              <div>
                <strong>已有 Node.js？</strong>執行 <code>node --version</code>。如果是 v22 或以上就沒問題。
                舊版本請用 <code>brew upgrade node</code> 升級，或使用
                <a href="https://github.com/nvm-sh/nvm" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">nvm</a> 切換版本。
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section id="openclaw" class="article-section">
            <h2>第三步：安裝 OpenClaw</h2>
            <p>透過 npm 全域安裝 OpenClaw CLI：</p>
            <pre><code>npm install -g openclaw@latest</code></pre>
            <p class="code-hint">⌨️ 複製貼上後，按 Enter 鍵確認執行</p>

            <div class="terminal-preview">
              <div class="terminal-bar">
                <span class="dot dot-red"></span>
                <span class="dot dot-yellow"></span>
                <span class="dot dot-green"></span>
                <span class="terminal-title">Terminal — bash</span>
              </div>
              <pre class="terminal-body"><code><span class="t-prompt">$</span> npm install -g openclaw@latest
added 312 packages in 18s
<span class="t-success">✔</span> OpenClaw 安裝成功！

<span class="t-prompt">$</span> openclaw --version
openclaw/2.4.1 darwin-arm64 node-v22.14.0</code></pre>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section id="setup" class="article-section">
            <h2>第四步：執行設定</h2>

            <StepCard number="4a" title="執行引導精靈">
              <pre><code>openclaw onboard --install-daemon</code></pre>
              <p class="code-hint">⌨️ 複製貼上後，按 Enter 鍵確認執行</p>
              <p>互動式精靈會引導你完成：</p>
              <ul>
                <li>選擇 AI 供應商（建議 Anthropic Claude）</li>
                <li>輸入 API Key</li>
                <li>設定工作目錄（預設：<code>~/.openclaw/workspace</code>）</li>
                <li>安裝 macOS LaunchAgent 背景服務（登入後自動啟動）</li>
              </ul>
              <div class="tip-box">
                <strong>💡 API Key：</strong>到
                <a href="https://console.anthropic.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">console.anthropic.com</a>
                取得 Anthropic API Key。新帳號有 $5 免費額度，足夠入門使用。
              </div>
            </StepCard>

            <StepCard number="4b" title="啟動 Gateway">
              <pre><code>openclaw gateway --port 18789</code></pre>
              <p class="code-hint">⌨️ 複製貼上後，按 Enter 鍵確認執行</p>
              <p>你會看到：</p>
              <pre><code>✔ Gateway running at http://127.0.0.1:18789/
✔ Agent: My Assistant (Claude 3.5 Sonnet)
✔ Daemon: active</code></pre>
              <p>在 Safari 或 Chrome 開啟 <a href="http://127.0.0.1:18789" target="_blank">http://127.0.0.1:18789</a> 即可看到控制台。</p>
            </StepCard>

            <StepCard number="4c" title="連接第一個頻道">
              <p>連接 Telegram、WhatsApp 或 Discord：</p>
              <pre><code>openclaw channels login</code></pre>
              <p class="code-hint">⌨️ 複製貼上後，按 Enter 鍵確認執行</p>
              <p>
                建議先看 <a href="/zh/guide/telegram">Telegram 連接教學</a> — 5 分鐘內可搞定。
              </p>
              <div class="success-box">
                <strong>✅ 完成！</strong>OpenClaw 已在你的 Mac 上以背景服務方式運行，重開機後自動啟動。
              </div>
            </StepCard>
          </section>

          <section id="faq" class="article-section">
            <h2>常見問題</h2>
            <div class="faq-list">
              <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-q" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                  需要讓 Terminal 保持開啟嗎？
                  <span class="faq-arrow">▼</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-a">
                  <p>不需要。使用 <code>--install-daemon</code> 安裝後，OpenClaw 會以 macOS LaunchAgent 在背景運行。關掉 Terminal 也沒關係，AI 照常服務。</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-q" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                  如何停止或重啟 OpenClaw？
                  <span class="faq-arrow">▼</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-a">
                  <pre><code>openclaw gateway stop
openclaw gateway restart</code></pre>
<p class="code-hint">⌨️ 複製貼上後，按 Enter 鍵確認執行</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-q" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                  如何更新 OpenClaw？
                  <span class="faq-arrow">▼</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-a">
                  <pre><code>npm install -g openclaw@latest
openclaw gateway restart</code></pre>
<p class="code-hint">⌨️ 複製貼上後，按 Enter 鍵確認執行</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="support-note">
              遇到問題了嗎？加入 <a href="https://discord.com/invite/clawd" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">OpenClaw Discord 社群</a> 或 <a href="https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">回報問題</a>。
            </div>
          </section>

          <div class="nav-buttons">
            <a href="/zh/guide/install" class="btn btn-outline">← 選擇平台</a>
            <a href="/zh/guide/telegram" class="btn btn-primary">下一步：選擇通訊平台 →</a>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero { background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,107,53,0.08) 0%, transparent 100%); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 4rem 0 3rem; }
  .page-hero .badge { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .page-hero h1 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .page-subtitle { font-size: 1.1rem; max-width: 600px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .lang-notice { margin-top: 1rem; }
  .lang-notice a { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; }

  .page-content { padding: 3rem 0 5rem; }
  .content-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr; gap: 3rem; align-items: start; }
  .toc-inner { position: sticky; top: 84px; background: var(--bg2); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.25rem; }
  .toc-title { font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--text2); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .toc ul { list-style: none; }
  .toc li { margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .toc a { color: var(--text2); font-size: 0.875rem; }
  .toc a:hover { color: var(--accent); opacity: 1; }

  .article-section { margin-bottom: 3.5rem; }
  .article-section h2 { font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; padding-bottom: 0.75rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .article-section p { margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; }
  .article-section ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0.75rem 0 1rem; }
  .article-section ul li { padding: 0.3rem 0 0.3rem 1.5rem; position: relative; color: var(--text2); font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .article-section ul li::before { content: "→"; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--accent); }
  .article-section pre { margin: 1rem 0; }

  .requirements-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .req-card { background: var(--bg2); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.25rem; text-align: center; }
  .req-icon { font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .req-label { font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--text2); margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
  .req-value { font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
  .req-note { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--text2); }

  .info-box, .tip-box, .success-box { display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; padding: 1rem 1.25rem; border-radius: var(--radius); margin: 1.25rem 0; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6; }
  .info-box { background: rgba(0,212,255,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(0,212,255,0.2); color: var(--text2); }
  .info-icon { font-size: 1.1rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .tip-box { background: rgba(255,107,53,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(255,107,53,0.2); color: var(--text2); }
  .success-box { background: rgba(0,200,100,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(0,200,100,0.2); color: var(--text2); }

  .terminal-preview { background: #0d1117; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); overflow: hidden; margin: 1.25rem 0; }
  .terminal-bar { background: #161b22; padding: 0.6rem 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #30363d; }
  .dot { width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 50%; }
  .dot-red { background: #ff5f57; }
  .dot-yellow { background: #febc2e; }
  .dot-green { background: #28c840; }
  .terminal-title { font-size: 0.78rem; color: #8b949e; margin-left: 0.5rem; font-family: var(--mono); }
  .terminal-body { background: #0d1117; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; margin: 0; border: none; border-radius: 0; font-size: 0.83rem; line-height: 1.7; }
  .terminal-body code { background: none; color: #e6edf3; padding: 0; }
  .t-prompt { color: #58a6ff; }
  .t-success { color: #3fb950; }

  .faq-list { margin-top: 1rem; }

  .advanced-details { margin: 1.25rem 0; background: var(--bg2); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; font-size: 0.9rem; }
  .advanced-details summary { cursor: pointer; color: var(--text2); font-weight: 600; user-select: none; }
  .advanced-details summary:hover { color: var(--accent); }
  .advanced-content { padding-top: 0.75rem; color: var(--text2); line-height: 1.7; }
  .support-note { margin-top: 1.5rem; padding: 1rem 1.25rem; background: var(--bg2); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text2); }
  .support-note a { color: var(--accent); }

  .nav-buttons { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); margin-top: 1rem; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .content-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .toc { display: none; }
    .requirements-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 500px) {
    .requirements-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .nav-buttons { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
  }


  /* Mobile layout hardening for install pages */
  .page-hero .container,
  .page-content .container { padding-left: 1rem; padding-right: 1rem; }
  .article,
  .article-section,
  .terminal-preview,
  .tip-box,
  .info-box,
  .success-box,
  .warning-box,
  .error-box,
  .support-note,
  .advanced-details,
  .tailscale-box { max-width: 100%; }
  .article pre,
  .article code,
  .terminal-body,
  pre code { overflow-x: auto; max-width: 100%; -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-content .container { max-width: 48rem; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; padding-left: 1rem; padding-right: 1rem; }
    .article-section { margin-bottom: 2.4rem; }
  }
</style>
